modName: Wintertide Rustic Performance ENB - needs original
summary: This is a strong and performance friendly and rustic ENB based off the Wintertide - Fantasy ENB by WoodManGamer.
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://img198.imageshack.us/img198/4120/headerfinalb.jpg[/IMG]

Firstly, all credit goes to [b]WoodManGamer[/b] and those who he acknowledged for making the original [b][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28176]Wintertide - Fantasy ENB[/url][/b] , and thanks to him for allowing me to upload an edited performance version.

You MUST download the [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28176]Wintertide - Fantasy ENB[/url] - this is ONLY the enbseries.ini file. 

Installation instructions are in the downloads. This is compatible with the [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15123]HiAlgo Performance Boost[/url].

[b]IMPORTANT[/b] - I have made and tested this with the performance version ONLY, using the Quality option can return unexpected results. Depth of field is not included in this. I used Dynavision (link at bottom). The images contain other mods, listed at the bottom too.

The frame rate drop pretty small, I lost about 3/5 FPS, so this is pretty performance friendly.

The sun effect is strong, I did intend for this. Looking at the sun straight has a lot of glare. It is my first ENB edit so all positive criticism is welcomed.

Once again, the credit goes to WoodManGamer.

Also, a thanks for all those who\'s mods I used in the screenshots

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168]ApachiiSkyHair[/url] - thank you apachii
